# Code owners for The Sopranos Wiki
#
# Branch protection on `main` requires code-owner review, so @joedef is
# automatically requested on every pull request and must approve before it
# can merge. The catch-all below covers the whole repository; the more
# specific entries exist to document intent, not to change who reviews.

# Everything
*                       @joedef

# Site configuration, build, and deployment — changes here can break the
# published site or the release process.
/mkdocs.yml             @joedef
/requirements.txt       @joedef
/.github/               @joedef
/overrides/             @joedef
/scripts/               @joedef
/docs/assets/           @joedef

# Licensing and contribution terms
/LICENSE                @joedef
/LICENSE-CONTENT.md     @joedef
/CONTRIBUTING.md        @joedef
